<--- JS stacktrace --->                                                                                                                                        
                                                                               
FATAL ERROR: MarkCompactCollector: young object promotion failed Allocation failed - JavaScript heap out of memory  
```

### How often does it reproduce? Is there a required condition?

Every time.

